Comment: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,原本已經被咬斷的手和腳...
Comment: 0,0:21:41.53,0:21:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,還在...
Comment: 0,0:21:42.87,0:21:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,艾連在當時...
Comment: 0,0:21:45.06,0:21:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,被巨人吞下肚...
Comment: 0,0:21:48.10,0:21:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,那個時候...
Comment: 0,0:21:58.72,0:21:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,到底...
Comment: 0,0:22:00.35,0:22:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,發生了什麼...
Comment: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,難道這都是艾連...
Comment: 0,0:22:13.54,0:22:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,幹的事情嗎...?
Comment: 0,0:22:15.24,0:22:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,ED
Comment: 0,0:23:53.26,0:23:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,消滅巨人
Comment: 0,0:23:55.73,0:23:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,karaoke,這份強烈的信念使艾連變成巨人
